<li>put drag handles in front of zoom buttons, so that drag handles are still accessible when they overlap zoom buttons
<li>constrain dragging of bars so that pH remains in range -1 to 15
<li>fix vertical alignment of pH slider ticks and bar graph ticks
<li>rename "soda" to "soda pop"
<li>make beaker's minor tick marks noticeably short than major tick marks
